HEADLESS DISCIPLINE (the reason this task exists): you are a one-shot headless run. Everything must complete SYNCHRONOUSLY inside your own process before you stop responding. NEVER spawn background jobs to "wait for later", never say you will wait for a notification - there are none. A prior agent (07c) made exactly that mistake.
